 <title>Troubleshooting PHP on Windows</title>
 <sect2>
  <title>Check Temp Directory Permissions</title>

  <procedure>
   <step>
    <para>
     Right-click the temp directory in File Explorer to get the permissions.
    </para>
   </step>
   <step>
    <para>
     For IIS, check that user IIS_User has MODIFY permission.
     The temporary directory is available from the configuration or <function>phpinfo</function>.
    </para>
   </step>
  </procedure>
 </sect2>
</sect1>
